OL,3,CLord Houchen secures third term as
OL,4,CTees Valley Mayor with reduced majority
OL,6,FConservative peer Lord Houchen has
OL,7,Fsecured a third mayoral term in the
OL,8,FTees Valley - but with a reduced
OL,9,Fmajority.
OL,11,FHe won a total of 81,930 votes across
OL,12,Fthe Tees Valley, while Labour
OL,13,Fcandidate Chris McEwan - his nearest
OL,14,Frival - polled 63,141 votes.
OL,16,FLord Houchen was first elected to the
OL,17,Frole in May 2017 in a surprise
OL,18,Fvictory. He was re-elected in 2021
OL,19,Fwith 72.8% of the vote.
