OL,3,CLord Houchen secures third term as
OL,4,CTees Valley Mayor with reduced majority
OL,6,F"Teesside is a place where I was born,
OL,7,Fwhere I grew up and other than a
OL,8,Fsabbatical to Newcastle for four years
OL,9,Fwhen I came straight back, it's a
OL,10,Fplace where I am going to be for the
OL,11,Frest of my life.
OL,13,F"To be reelected for a third term in
OL,14,Fmy home, in my community is absolutely
OL,15,Fthe greatest honour that anyone could
OL,16,Fever give me.
OL,18,F"Let's be clear, there's a still a
OL,19,Flong way to go. I'm not sat here
OL,20,Fpretending that everything's perfect
OL,21,Fbur t we are making good progress.
