OL,3,CLord Houchen secures third term as
OL,4,CTees Valley Mayor with reduced majority
OL,6,F"We need to continue to tackle the
OL,7,Fproblems that we have in our local
OL,8,Farea. The plan that I've got in place
OL,9,Fis the right one. As long as I'm
OL,10,Fmayor, I will continue to work as hard
OL,11,Fas I can for everybody."
OL,13,FThe result comes on a bruising night
OL,14,Ffor the Conservative party in the
OL,15,Flocal elections across the country and
OL,16,Facross the North East with Labour
OL,17,Fmaking gains in areas like Hartlepool
OL,18,Fwhere they took over the running of
OL,19,Fthe council.
