OL,4,CTees Valley Mayor with reduced majority
OL,6,FLord Houchen also said he will provide
OL,7,Ffree swimming for children under 11
OL,8,Fand introduce more flights from
OL,9,FTeesside Airport - one of his passion
OL,10,Fprojects as mayor - "to places like
OL,11,FMalaga and Tenerife."
OL,13,FA key part of Lord Houchen's tenure
OL,14,Fhas been the development of Teesworks
OL,15,Faround Redcar's former steelworks.
