OL,3,CLord Houchen secures third term as
OL,4,CTees Valley Mayor with reduced majority
OL,6,FFollowing the declaration, John
OL,7,FMcCabe, chief executive at the North
OL,8,FEast Chamber of Commerce, said:
OL,9,F"Congratulations to Ben Houchen on his
OL,10,Fre-election as Tees Valley mayor. In
OL,11,Fhis first two terms and throughout
OL,12,Fthis campaign, Mayor Houchen has
OL,13,Fplaced an emphasis on economic
OL,14,Fdevelopment.
OL,16,F"I hope that in his third term, we can
OL,17,Fwork ever more closely with the mayor
OL,18,Fand his team to ensure the benefits of
OL,19,Fdevolution are felt by all businesses
OL,20,Fand all communities across the Tees
OL,21,FValley."
